title: ISic001273. I.Sicily inscription 001273
body:
Facsimile Images

[ἱερατεύσασαν τᾶς Ἀφ]ροδίτας
[------]στράτου
[ἀνέθηκεν ἁ β]ουλὰ καὶ
[ὁ δᾶμος τᾶι Ἀφρο]δίται

Apparatus criticus

Text of IG

English translation

... was priestess of Aphrodite, the council and the people dedicated (this) to Aphrodite.
